videos.description: Jalani Eason throws 42 yds to Josh Kraght for  a touchdown early in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Eason connects with Kraght for Portland State TD

videos.description: Ryan Nall runs it in for a 1 yd touchdown in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Nall's TD puts Oregon State ahead

videos.description: Jalani Eason puts Portland State on the one-yard line with a 40-yard run.
videos.headline: Eason breaks off 40-yard run

videos.description: Garretson runs the ball in from four yards for a Oregon State touchdown late in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Garretson extends Oregon State's lead with TD run

videos.description: Jalani Eason scores a 5-yard TD on the QB draw.
videos.headline: Portland State closes gap with rushing TD

videos.description: Beau Duronslet recovers fumble to give Vikings great field position.

videos.headline: Eason's second TD run gives Portland State the lead

videos.description: Noah Togiai's 48-yard catch and run sets up Oregon State first and goal.
videos.headline: Luton connects with Togiai on a 48-yard pass

videos.description: Manase Hungalu return's the interception 21 yards  for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Hungalu's pick-six extends lead for Oregon State

videos.description: Josh Kraght's second touchdown catch brings the Vikings within a score of the Beavers.
videos.headline: Portland State closes the gap with Kraght's TD

videos.headline: Portland State reclaims the lead with Kraght's TD run
